You have done much to aid the Host of the West since the march from Minas Tirith. You traversed the Ruins of Osgiliath. You braved the Wilds of Ithilien. You endured the Harshness of The Wastes. If not for your help, the Host of the West may not have been able to stand at the gates of Mordor and overcome the odds.
